DVC spec fixtures — attribution
================================

`hancom_test.json` and `hancom_full.json` are verbatim copies of

    sample/test.json         (from hancom-io/dvc, committed as hancom_test.json)
    sample/jsonFullSpec.json (from hancom-io/dvc, committed as hancom_full.json)

sourced from https://github.com/hancom-io/dvc.

